name: chomik
description: Chomik is about the characters virality and cuteness. Born as the mascot of a popular Web2 Polish File share program, he was made to visualise stages of the process, he is more than an hourglass.. he is memetic gold that fits in everywhere. Chomik is the narrative, the more you see him, the more timeless this age of web2 animorphisation becomes. Tech is functional, Chomik makes that tech fun and relatable.
